---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout title="Book Title">
	<main class="mx-auto mb-24 max-w-screen-xl grow px-4 sm:px-6">
		<div class="flex flex-col lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-8">
			<div class="md:max-w-1xl md:mx-auto lg:col-span-8">
				<h1
					class="mb-12 mt-1 text-4xl font-extrabold uppercase leading-10 tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl sm:leading-none lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl"
				>
					Food For <span class="underline">All.</span>
				</h1>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-bold uppercase">Let's Seed U.P.</h2>
				<p
					class="mb-6 mt-3 font-body text-base text-gray-500 sm:mt-2 sm:text-xl lg:text-lg"
				>
					Letâ€™s Seed U.P.! is a seed distribution/garden building and support
					project funded through a grant provided by District 10.
					<a href="/hunger/programs#lets-seed-up">Click for REAL details!</a>
				</p>

				<h2 class="text-xl font-bold uppercase">Kids Backpack Program</h2>
				<p
					class="mb-6 mt-3 font-body text-base text-gray-500 sm:mt-2 sm:text-xl lg:text-lg"
				>
					D10 Hunger's mission is to fight against hunger by providing food
					&amp; life-changing aid. We've realized that schools are the perfect
					target for the Backpack program - they are the gathered location for
					children in need. <a href="/hunger/programs#kids-backpack-program"
						>Click for REAL details!</a
					>
				</p>

				<h2 class="text-xl font-bold uppercase">
					UP Food As Medicine/UP Fresh Food Access Program
				</h2>
				<p
					class="mb-6 mt-3 font-body text-base text-gray-500 sm:mt-2 sm:text-xl lg:text-lg"
				>
					...is a practice built on the knowledge that food and diet play
					important roles in disease prevention and management by prioritizing
					food and diet in an individual&#39;s health plan, with the goal of
					overall health. <a href="/hunger/programs#food-as-medicine"
						>Click for REAL details!</a
					>
				</p>

				<h2 class="text-xl font-bold uppercase">
					Emergency Food Transportation
				</h2>
				<p
					class="mb-6 mt-3 font-body text-base text-gray-500 sm:mt-2 sm:text-xl lg:text-lg"
				>
					In an emergency situation, access to food resources is critical. The
					ability to transport food from one location to individuals and
					families in need in a community is our goal. <a
						href="/hunger/programs#emergency-food-transportation"
						>Click for REAL details!</a
					>
				</p>

				<div class="grow">
					<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-book-gray sm:mt-5 sm:text-base">
						For any of the above, we gladly accept donations directly through
						this site!
						<a href="https://donorbox.org/lions-hunger" target="_blank">
							Please consider helping us with financial support!</a
						>
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div
				id="hero-image"
				class="relative mt-12 h-60 w-full rounded-2xl bg-center object-contain sm:mx-auto lg:col-span-4 lg:mx-0 lg:mt-0 lg:h-full lg:max-w-none lg:items-center lg:rounded-tl-[200px]"
			>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	#hero-image {
		background-image: url("/hunger/hero.jpg");
	}

	#hero-image::after {
		content: "";
		display: block;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		position: absolute;
		z-index: -1;
		background-color: #f37728;
		border-radius: 15px;
		transform: translateY(5%) scale(1.02);
	}

	@media (min-width: 1024px) {
		#hero-image::after {
			height: 90%;
			bottom: 0;
			border-top-left-radius: 200px;
			transform: translate(-8%) scale(0.95);
		}
	}
</style>
